Tie/FileHandle/Base version 0.1
================================

A base module to simplify creation of new FileHandle Tie modules by
noting redundancies in the required functions.  Currently supports
only output tie modules.  Input support is forthcoming.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

